    • Constructor Detail

      • SlaEventSubmitter

        public SlaEventSubmitter(EventSubmitter submitter,
                         java.lang.String name,
                         java.util.Properties props)
        Construct an SlaEventSubmitter by extracting Sla event metadata from the properties. See SlaEventKeys for keys to set in properties

        Use SlaEventSubmitter#builder() to build an SlaEventSubmitter directly with event metadata.

        Parameters:
        submitter - used to submit the event
        name - of the event
        props - reference that contains event metadata

    • Method Detail

      • submit

        public void submit()
        Submit the sla event by calling SlaEventSubmitter#EventSubmitter#submit(). If eventName, eventSubmitter, datasetUrn , partition are not available the method is a no-op.
